nclawzero-rdp-init (1.0.0-1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian packaging (ported from Yocto recipe).
  * First-boot service: generates self-signed TLS cert for Weston RDP
    backend and seeds pi user password from /etc/nclawzero/initial-password.
  * Idempotent via /var/lib/nclawzero/rdp-init.done sentinel.

